import os
from pathlib import Path
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
try:
    import google.colab
    IN_COLAB = True
except:
    IN_COLAB = False
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
if IN_COLAB:
    from google.colab import drive
    drive.mount('/gdrive')

    %cd /gdrive/'My Drive'

    # set up a folders for images
    path_img_aug=Path('gx-pokedex/card_images/augmented')
else:
    path_img_aug=Path(f"{os.environ['HOME']}/Google Drive/card_images/augmented")
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
from fastai.vision import *
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
data = ImageDataBunch.from_folder(path_img_aug, train='.', valid_pct=0.2, ds_tfms=get_transforms(), size=224).normalize(imagenet_stats)
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
data.show_batch(rows=4, figsize=(7,8))
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
learn = cnn_learner(data, models.resnet34, metrics=error_rate)
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
learn.fit_one_cycle(4)
0.00% [0/4 00:00<00:00]
epoch train_loss valid_loss error_rate time

0.25% [1/408 02:29<16:56:30 6.7569]
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
learn.save('stage-1')
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
learn.unfreeze() # must be done before calling lr_find
learn.lr_find()
learn.recorder.plot()
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
learn.unfreeze()
learn.fit_one_cycle(2, max_lr=slice(6e-5,3e-4))
learn.save('stage-2')
